LogicalTable.name: F0 Sales Base Measures
LogicalTable.Description: This logical table contains metrics like Revenue, Billed Qty, Booked Amt and Booked Qty with different types of aggregation like Sum, First on Time , Last on Time and Count Distinct. All the metrics in this table are physically mapped to columns in the Revenue fact table.

LogicalColumn.name: 1- Revenue
LogicalColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Dollars physical column in FactsRev table joining to time using Billed time.
- Returns sum of data over any selected dimensions
